(97, '\r\n “Tai nạn của siêu mẫu” là clip nổi bật nhất Internet tuần qua', '', '\r\n <div align="center"><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;"><object id="PlayerAS0256e43470024bd0b0ae2d70ea1f1375" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" height="334" width="425"><embed wmode="transparent" quality="high" bgcolor="#425166" flashvars="" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" name="0256e43470024bd0b0ae2d70ea1f1375" id="0256e43470024bd0b0ae2d70ea1f1375" style="" src="http://cache.hosting.vcmedia.vn/?key=0256e43470024bd0b0ae2d70ea1f1375&amp;pname=mediaplayer.swf&amp;img=http://video-thumbs.vcmedia.vn/dantri/tI0YUx18mEaF5kMsGHJxA/2013/04/video-010-df1ed.jpg" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" height="334" width="425"></object><br>Siêu mẫu Hàn Quốc tuột váy trong lúc chạy<br><br><object id="PlayerASd24616cf610542b999546eecc1fd4f46" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" height="334" width="425"><param name="movie" value="http://cache.hosting.vcmedia.vn/?key=d24616cf610542b999546eecc1fd4f46&amp;pname=mediaplayer.swf&amp;img=http://video-thumbs.vcmedia.vn/dantri/tI0YUx18mEaF5kMsGHJxA/2013/04/video-01-e945e.jpg"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"><param value="#425166" name="bgcolor"><param name="wmode" value="transparent"><embed wmode="transparent" quality="high" bgcolor="#425166" flashvars="" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" name="d24616cf610542b999546eecc1fd4f46" id="d24616cf610542b999546eecc1fd4f46" style="" src="http://cache.hosting.vcmedia.vn/?key=d24616cf610542b999546eecc1fd4f46&amp;pname=mediaplayer.swf&amp;img=http://video-thumbs.vcmedia.vn/dantri/tI0YUx18mEaF5kMsGHJxA/2013/04/video-01-e945e.jpg" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" height="334" width="425"></object><br>Người thanh niên nát tay vì trêu cá sấu <br><br><object id="PlayerAS0e6647e964e949a9b60077f08c58401b" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" height="334" width="425